title: Free instructions for the Joe Cell
description:
The Joe Cell is one of the only available fuel cells, that you can power your vehicle soley from converting water to hydrogen. The invention was threated and now the instructions are available for free.  The instructions are easy to read and construction of the Joe cell should be done by a professional.  Get some help!
The inventor should be rewarded for his work somehow, there is lots of information on water to hydrogen on youtube.  Please seed this .pdf and share it as many people as possible.  check out the MYT motor on youtube well over 100 mpg
